# Exercise

<div id="outcomes"><details><summary></summary>

* Trace the operation of Floyd's heapify method, which builds the heap from the bottom up.

</details></div>

<span class="tag">Exercise</span> Heapify the following collection (sequence of numbers) using Floyds method. Draw the binary heap and corresponding rank array representation as in the previous demo.

$$
8, 3, 2, 7, 9, 4
$$

